/** Author: Isaiah Jeter Contact Info: ijeter@g.hmc.edu Last Updated: 09/02/25 Summary: Instantiates the led controller and 7-segment display controller for lab 1 */ module top( input logic [3:0] switches, output logic [6:0] seg,
output logic [2:0] led
);
segControl segment(switches, seg); ledControl ledcontroller(switches, led); endmodule
